   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00010"/>Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb45277" type="place">Mariä Schutz</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">am <rs ref="#pmb189" type="place">Semmering</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00009"/><hi rend="pre-print">Blick auf <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1100">Schloss Welsberg</rs>
                  vom <rs type="place" ref="#pmb723">Hôtel Wildbad Waldbrunn</rs> aus</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00009"/>Sind<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eit 8 Tagen hier, fühlen uns<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr behaglich, bleiben voraus<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ichtlich den ganzen
                  So<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>er. Ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern ist <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12692">Heini</rs> nachgeko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en.</p><p>La<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr bald von<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich hören.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer><postscript><p>Viele Grüße von Uns an Sie Alle.</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
